<center><h1><span class="Black">About The Game</span></h1></center>
<center><p>Game Thingy is a 2D mining game where you go mining underground in search of valuable gems and minerals.
While mining for gems and minerals, you may come across minesafts along the way. In the minesafts, you may find treasure chests
which may contains valuable minerals and gems or gold coins. With the minerals and gems that you've mined and found in chests can be sold for gold coins. With the coins you've earned, 
you use them to buy upgrades like better pickaxes and so on.<p>
<center><h1><span class="Black">System Requirements</h1></center>
<center><p>Any system that is from the last 10-15 years.</p></center>
